text: This synt þa landgemære to Duntune.
Ærest of þære readan hane on fobban wylle.
Þonon on crawanlea on eblesburnan.
Andlang burnan on meorh þorn, þonon on ceorla hlæwe.
Of ceorla hlæwe on crawan crundel.
Þonon on fyrdinges lea.
Of þam lea on eblesburnan.
Andlang burnan utt on afene.
Up ofer afene on earnes beorh.
Þonon andlang hæmedes weges on haseloran.
Þonon on wendenes wyrðe.
Of wendænes wyrðæ thweores ofer þane holt to laneforda.
Of laneforda æft on þa readan hane.
Ðis synt þara XXX hida landgemæra on wiht þe þærto hyrad.
Ærest of sæ up on æscstede.
Þonon on þone gemotbeorh.
Of þam beorge on swines heafod.
Þonon on suðsæ.
Upp of þære suðsæ on Eadgylses muþan.
Andlang Eadgylses muþan on bican dæne.
Þonon on Cawelburnan.
Andlang Cawelburnan utt on norð sæ.
